'''2011年挪威爆炸和枪击事件'''、'''烏托亞島大屠殺'''，是指2011年7月22日发生在[[挪威|挪威]]首都[[奥斯陆|奥斯陆]]市的爆炸事件与数小时后发生在[[于特岛|于特岛]]的枪击事件。[[欧洲中部夏令时间|当地时间]]15时26分，位于[[奥斯陆|奥斯陆]]市中心的挪威政府办公大楼附近发生爆炸，挪威政府大楼、财政部大楼以及对面的《世界之路》报社在爆炸中受到破坏，造成8人死亡，30人受伤<ref>{{cite web |language = zh-cn |publisher = 网易 |title = 挪威首都大楼爆炸案已有2人死亡多人受伤 |url = http://news.163.com/11/0722/21/79JMC0IL00014JB5.html |date = 2011-07-22 |accessdate = 2011-07-23 |archive-date = 2021-01-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210109064012/https://news.163.com/11/0722/21/79JMC0IL00014JB5.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。在炸彈爆炸發生2小時後，在位于奥斯陆以西约40公里处[[于特岛|于特岛]]发生枪击事件，一名装扮成警察的枪手向在岛上参加執政[[挪威工黨|挪威工黨]]举办的{{le|挪威工党青年团|Workers' Youth League (Norway)|青年团}}的人群射击，69人死亡<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vg.no/nyheter/innenriks/oslobomben/artikkel.php?artid=10080770 |title=Police scale down: 68 killed in Utøya |date=25 July 2011 |publisher=[[VG_Nett|VG Nett]] |language=no |accessdate=25 July 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111114044739/http://www.vg.no/nyheter/innenriks/oslobomben/artikkel.php?artid=10080770 |archivedate=2011-11-14 }}</ref>，打伤66人，疑犯當場被捕。

枪手是32岁的挪威人[[安德斯·贝林·布雷维克|安德斯·贝林·布雷维克]]。當地警方证实两起袭击事件係安德斯一人所为，且与国际恐怖主义组织无关<ref>{{cite web|author=高轶军|title=挪威爆炸枪击事件系“本土男子所为”与国际恐怖组织无关|url=http://world.people.com.cn/GB/15228072.html|publisher=人民网|accessdate=2011-07-23|archive-date=2020-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427075357/http://world.people.com.cn/GB/15228072.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。總共有77人死於該兩宗襲擊。

本次袭击事件是挪威自[[二战|二战]]時受[[威瑟演習行動|德國軍事入侵]]后70年間遭受的最大规模袭击，也是[[马德里三一一爆炸案|2004年马德里连环爆炸案]]和[[倫敦七七爆炸案|2005年伦敦爆炸案]]后欧洲最严重的屠杀事件<ref>{{cite web|title=记者连线:挪威奥斯陆爆炸枪击事件震惊欧洲|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2011-07/23/c_121711454.htm|publisher=新华网|accessdate=2011-07-24|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117064724/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2011-07/23/c_121711454.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 奥斯陆爆炸事件 ==
[[File:2011_Oslo_attacks_map.svg|thumb]]
2011年7月22日15时26分左右（[[欧洲中部夏令时间|欧洲中部夏令时间]]），挪威奥斯陆市中心的挪威政府总部办公楼群H楼（Høyblokka）与R4楼之间的Grubbegata道发生强力爆炸。爆炸地点紧邻挪威首相办公室（位于H楼内）及另一些政府部门如{{link-en|挪威石油和能源部|Ministry of Petroleum and Energy (Norway)}}（R4楼）、[[挪威財政部|挪威財政部]]（G楼）等等。

据当时现场附近的办公人员回忆，至少听见两声接连的爆炸声<ref name="NYT1">{{cite web | title =At Least 80 Dead in Norway Shooting | url =http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/23/world/europe/23oslo.html | author =LISA MALA, J. DAVID GOODMAN | date =2011-07-22 | publisher =[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] | accessdate =2011-07-23 | archive-date =2011-07-24 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20110724004316/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/23/world/europe/23oslo.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>。爆炸声音震破了400米外的窗户玻璃，4公里外都可听到<ref name="BBCL">{{cite web | title =As it happened: Norway attacks | url =http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14254705 | date =2011-07-22 | publisher =[[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC新闻]] | accessdate =2011-07-23 | archive-date =2011-07-22 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20110722170637/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14254705 | dead-url =no }}</ref>。爆炸后，附近建筑的窗户玻璃几乎全部震破。事发道路上满是瓦砾与玻璃碎片。临近的H楼的低层建筑与R4楼严重受损。H楼高层有黑色浓烟冒出，R4楼低层持续着火并有白色浓烟冒出，直达数十米高度<ref name="NYT1"/>。道路中可见到汽车的残骸（左图橙色区域）<ref name="bombBBC">{{cite web | title =Oslo: Bomb blast near Norway prime minister's office | url =http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14252515 | date =2011-07-22 | publisher =[[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC新闻]] | accessdate =2011-07-23 | archive-date =2011-07-22 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20110722170627/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14252515 | dead-url =no }}</ref>。有不止一人浑身浴血倒在路上。警方到场后确认至少有7人死亡，15人受伤，并封锁区域<ref name="NYT1"/>。

[[File:Statsministers_kontor_Office_of_the_prime_minister.jpg|thumb]]
附近在场民众普遍被爆炸震惊，不少人立即逃离现场。警方从受波及的建筑中运出数位伤者，并要求居民尽量疏散以及少使用手机<ref name="telegraph">{{cite web | title =Oslo explosion: seven dead, dozens injured after Norway city blast | url =http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/norway/8655120/Oslo-explosion-seven-dead-dozens-injured-after-Norway-city-blast.html | date =2011-07-22 | publisher =The Telegraph | accessdate =2011-07-23 | archive-date =2020-05-26 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200526132036/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/norway/8655120/Oslo-explosion-seven-dead-dozens-injured-after-Norway-city-blast.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

据奥斯陆代理警察局长斯朋海姆（Sveinung Sponheim）确认，爆炸案应是由汽车炸弹引起<ref name="BBC2">{{cite web | title =Norway mourns twin attack victims | url =http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14262956 | date =2011-07-23 | publisher =BBC News | accessdate =2011-07-23 | archive-date =2020-11-12 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20201112003134/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14262956 | dead-url =no }}</ref>。他认为临近大楼内可能还有尸体或未引爆的爆炸物，但由于建筑处于危险状态而暂时无法搜查<ref name="BBC2"/>。

=== 伤亡情况 ===
警方最初确认2人死亡，不久后增加至7人，并有15人严重受伤，其中11人情况危殆需要立即送院治疗。此外有约100人轻度受伤需要治疗。绝大多数伤者是被坠落的杂物与玻璃所伤，受伤部位多在头部和胸部<ref name="USAT">{{cite web | title =17 dead in Oslo bombing, shootings; Norwegian held | url =http://content.usatoday.com/communities/ondeadline/post/2011/07/blast-in-oslo-blows-out-government-office-building-windows/1 | date =2011-07-22 | author =Michael Winter | publisher =[[今日美国|今日美国]] | accessdate =2011-07-23 | archive-date =2012-05-29 | archive-url =https://archive.is/20120529011914/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/ondeadline/post/2011/07/blast-in-oslo-blows-out-government-office-building-windows/1 | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

[[File:Skader_på_olje_og_energidepartementet.jpg|thumb]]
[[挪威首相|挪威首相]][[延斯·斯托尔滕贝格|延斯·斯托尔滕贝格]]当时不在办公室内，因此并未受到爆炸波及<ref name="USAT"/>。他在爆炸后一小时左右致电挪威{{link-en|TV2 (挪威)|TV 2 (Norway)|TV 2}}电视台，表示他本人处于安全状态，但因应警方建议，不便透露他所在位置。此外没有挪威政府官员在爆炸中受伤。政府官员汉斯·克里斯蒂安·阿芒森认为，由于事发当时是星期五下午，不少职员已经离开办公地点，否则受爆炸波及者可能会更多<ref name="BBCL"/>。

=== 交通影响 ===
[[File:Oslo_bomb_blast_July_22_2011_Image_01.JPG|thumb]]
事发后约20分钟，警方封锁了爆炸附近的区域，并疏散了附近人群。警方呼吁奥斯陆市内的居民不要靠近市中心区域，并称出于不确定是否会有更多的恐怖袭击的考虑，要求市民尽量少使用手机<ref name= Duxbury>{{cite news|last= Duxbury|first= Charles|title= Deadly Attacks Shake Norway|url= http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424053111903461104576461862078291234.html?mod=googlenews_wsj|accessdate= 2011-07-22|newspaper= [[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|date= 2011-07-22|archive-date= 2019-08-22|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190822090341/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424053111903461104576461862078291234|dead-url= no}}</ref>。与此同时，出入奥斯陆的公共交通工具暂时停运<ref>{{cite news|title= Oslo Bomb Attack — Eyewitness Reports|date= 2011-07-22|first= Jillian|last= Rayfield|work= LiveWire|url= http://tpmlivewire.talkingpointsmemo.com/2011/07/oslo-bomb-attack---eyewitness-reports.php|accessdate= 2011-07-22|publisher= Talking Points Memo|deadurl= yes|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110724070344/http://tpmlivewire.talkingpointsmemo.com/2011/07/oslo-bomb-attack---eyewitness-reports.php|archivedate= 2011-07-24}}</ref>。[[BBC|BBC]]（英国广播公司）称收到当地居民发出的电子邮件，称市内到奥斯陆机场的道路上已经架设了警方的检查点<ref name=bbc1>{{cite news| title = Oslo bomb — latest updates| date = 22 July 2011| publisher = [[英国广播公司|BBC]]| location = 英国| work = 新闻| url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14254705| accessdate = 2011-07-22| archive-date = 2011-07-22| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110722170637/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14254705| dead-url = no}}</ref>。而警方正在对机场内的车辆进行搜检<ref>{{cite news| title= Bomb blast rocks downtown Oslo| date= 2011-07-22| work= RT| url= http://rt.com/news/oslo-explosion-pm-headquarters/| accessdate= 2011-07-22| archive-date= 2020-10-24| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201024211835/https://www.rt.com/news/oslo-explosion-pm-headquarters/| dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Oslo-trikken: – Det er normal drift, ingen grunn til bekymring|date=2011-07-22|work=TV 2|location=NO|language=no|url=http://www.tv2.no/nyheter/innenriks/oslotrikken-det-er-normal-drift-ingen-grunn-til-bekymring-3544402.html|accessdate=2011-07-22|archive-date=2014-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140415023143/http://www.tv2.no/nyheter/innenriks/oslotrikken-det-er-normal-drift-ingen-grunn-til-bekymring-3544402.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

铁路方面，由于铁轨附近发现可疑的包裹，[[利勒斯特罗姆|利勒斯特罗姆]]到奥斯陆机场的沿线铁路已经暂时关闭<ref>{{cite news|title=All trains shut down after suspicious package|date=2011-07-22|work=Dagbladet|location=NO|url=http://www.dagbladet.no/2011/07/22/nyheter/innenriks/flytog/17418881/|accessdate=2011-07-22|archive-date=2016-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202110654/http://www.dagbladet.no/2011/07/22/nyheter/innenriks/flytog/17418881/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。16时12分，奥斯陆中央火车站临时关闭<ref name="BBCL"/>。

== 于特岛枪击事件 ==
[[于特岛|于特岛]]是位于[[奥斯陆|奥斯陆]]西北部、直线距离约36公里的[[蒂里湖|蒂里湖]]中的一个小岛。每年夏天，隶属执政党[[挪威工党|工党]]的“工人青年团”会在岛上组织为期5日的[[夏令营|夏令营]]活动，培养下一代的政治领袖<ref>{{cite web | title =於特島﹕ 培育政治領袖場地 | url =http://news.mingpao.com/20110724/gba4.htm | publisher =明報 | accessdate =2011-07-24 | date =2011-07-24 | archive-date =2020-06-27 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200627215151/http://news.mingpao.com/20110724/gba4.htm | dead-url =no }}</ref>。挪威警方表示，奥斯陆市中心的爆炸事件发生后约一个半小时，作警察打扮的[[安德斯·贝林·布雷维克|安德斯·贝林·布雷维克]]持枪<ref>{{cite news |title=袭击由本土极端分子制造 |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2011-07-24/023022865350.shtml |accessdate=2011-07-23 |publisher=新浪新闻中心 |date=2011-07-23 |archive-date=2020-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427075508/http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2011-07-24/023022865350.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>乘坐渡轮登上[[于特岛|于特岛]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Police: 91 youth campers dead in mass shooting, bombing in Norway|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/europe/07/22/norway.explosion/index.html?iref=NS1|accessdate=2011-07-23|newspaper=[[CNN|CNN]]|location=美国|date=2011-07-23|archive-date=2020-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427075513/http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/europe/07/22/norway.explosion/index.html?iref=NS1|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并声称自己是赶来执行任务的[[警察|警察]]（他乘坐渡轮时使用了“马丁·尼尔森”作为化名。一位16岁的幸存者在接受采访时表示，凶手从码头慢悠悠地向聚集人群走来，“30多岁，看起来像一个和蔼的普通警察。”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/nuoweibaozhaqiangji/content-3/detail_2011_07/23/7896188_0.shtml?_from_ralated |title=于特岛枪击幸存者：凶手看起来像和蔼的普通警察 |accessdate=2011-07-23 |archive-date=2020-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200526132135/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/nuoweibaozhaqiangji/content-3/detail_2011_07/23/7896188_0.shtml?_from_ralated |dead-url=no }}</ref>），因奥斯陆发生爆炸事件而需要对岛上人员进行例行检查。营中的青少年已经获知奥斯陆市中心的爆炸案，因此大部分人都集合在一起，一共约有600人在场。正在夏令营中活动的青少年相信了他的话并向其靠拢，他像警察一样要求大家站成一列<ref>{{cite news |title= Flere unge skutt og drept på Utøya |url= http://www.nrk.no/nyheter/norge/1.7723132 |agency= [[挪威广播公司|挪威广播公司]] |date= 2011-07-22 |accessdate= 2011-07-22 |archive-date= 2011-07-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110723192315/http://www.nrk.no/nyheter/norge/1.7723132 |dead-url= no }}</ref>，然后突然从包中取出手枪射击<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/nuoweibaozhaqiangji/content-3/detail_2011_07/23/7896423_0.shtml |title=于特岛血案枪手扮成警察要求人们站成一列 随后开枪 |accessdate=2011-07-23 |archive-date=2020-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200526132144/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/nuoweibaozhaqiangji/content-3/detail_2011_07/23/7896423_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。惊慌失措的青少年们四处逃散躲避。有人试图躲入石头或灌木丛后，有人爬上树木，也有人跳水逃生。枪手于是“追着他们”开枪。由于该岛离湖岸约800米，一些跳水逃生的人不幸被淹死。目击者称，枪手先向岛上人员射击，然后又掉转枪口射杀湖中的逃生者<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/nuoweibaozhaqiangji/content-3/detail_2011_07/23/7895660_0.shtml |title=挪威于特岛枪击案现场：许多人跳海逃生被淹死 |accessdate=2011-07-23 |archive-date=2020-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200526132149/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/nuoweibaozhaqiangji/content-3/detail_2011_07/23/7895660_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。据一位幸存者描述，枪手射击时十分冷静，十分清楚自己在干什么，他向其他人大喊：“马克思主义者们，你们都会死”<ref name="BBC3"/>。一些游泳逃生的人发现距离岸边过远后开始往回游，然后躲在岸边的礁石下。而枪手在约1小时后折返开枪，又造成不少人死亡<ref name="CNN1">{{cite news |title= survivors pretend to be dead |url= http://edition.cnn.com/video/?/video/world/2011/07/23/bpr.pracon.norway.survivor.cnn |agency= CNN新闻视频 |date= 2011-07-23 |accessdate= 2011-07-23 |archive-date= 2011-12-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20111203234425/http://edition.cnn.com/video/?%2Fvideo%2Fworld%2F2011%2F07%2F23%2Fbpr.pracon.norway.survivor.cnn |dead-url= no }}</ref>。大多数幸存者躲在岩石下或地下室等遮蔽处，透过手机短信相互交流以避免被枪手发现。挪威司法部下国家警察局的一名发言人声称大部分遇难者年龄在15至16岁之间<ref>{{cite news | title = Blasts and Gun Attack in Norway; 7 Dead | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/23/world/europe/23oslo.html?_r=1 | agency = [[纽约时报|纽约时报]] | date = 2011-07-22 | accessdate = 2011-07-22 | archive-date = 2020-12-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201206233923/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/23/world/europe/23oslo.html?_r=1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

挪威警方在枪击事件发生的一个半小时后<ref>{{cite news  |title=Man Held After 91 Killed In Norway Attacks  |url=http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/World-News/Norway-At-Least-17-Dead-In-Youth-Camp-Shooting-In-Utoya-And-Bomb-Attack-In-Oslo/Article/201107416035907?lpos=World_News_Top_Stories_Header_0&lid=ARTICLE_16035907_Norway%3A_At_Least_17_Dead_In_Youth_Camp_Shooting_In_Utoya_And_Bomb_Attack_In_Oslo  |agency=SKY News  |date=2011-07-23  |accessdate=2011-07-23  |archive-date=2019-08-22  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822090339/https://news.sky.com/?lpos=World_News_Top_Stories_Header_0&lid=ARTICLE_16035907_Norway:_At_Least_17_Dead_In_Youth_Camp_Shooting_In_Utoya_And_Bomb_Attack_In_Oslo  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>赶到现场。有报道称警方未能及时找到可用的直升机，于是决定开车至湖边，而之后又花费若干分钟找到可渡湖的船只<ref name="BBC3"/>。在此之前，枪手在岛上四处走动，并向逃竄或躲避的人开火。警方赶到后，枪手并未反抗，向警方投降<ref name="BBC3"/>。由于枪手装扮成警察，一些幸存者看到赶来支援的警察后要求警察首先放下武器，害怕警察向他们射击<ref name="CNN1"/>。

挪威首相原本预计会出席这次夏令营活动<ref name="BBC3">{{cite news |title=Norway police say 85 killed in island youth camp attack |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14259356 |agency=BBC新闻 |date=2011-07-23 |accessdate=2011-07-24 |archive-date=2017-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171225204253/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14259356 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
